{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/film-anime-city-hunter-kembali-hadir-di-tahun-2019/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Film Anime City Hunter Kembali Hadir di Tahun 2019","content":"<p>Di benak fans Indonesia, nama City Hunter punya makna berbeda. Ada <em>manga</em> dan <em>anime</em> karangan Tsukasa Hojo, film <em>live action</em> yang diperankan Jackie Chan, hingga drama Korea yang menampilkan Lee Minho dan Park Minyoung. Entah City Hunter mana yang paling berkesan buat kamu, tapi semuanya menceritakan petualangan seorang detektif urakan yang membela kebenaran dengan caranya sendiri.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49774\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49774\" data-attachment-id=\"49774\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-anime-city-hunter-kembali-hadir-di-tahun-2019/attachment/09-city-hunter/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-city-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"09-city-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-city-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-city-hunter.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49774 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-city-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"city hunter jackie chan\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-city-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/09-city-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49774\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Jackie Chan sebagai Ryo Saeba yang cosplay jadi Chun-Li. Serius!. Sumber: Youtube</p></div></p>\n<p>Di tahun 2019 nanti, nampaknya kisah City Hunter akan terus berlanjut. Studio <em>anime</em> Sunrise mengumumkan akan membuat film <em>anime</em> City Hunter baru yang akan tayang pada tanggal 8 Februari 2019. Film ini akan jadi <em>anime</em> City Hunter pertama dalam 20 tahun terakhir.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4TnImjHwb7U\" width=\"667\" height=\"375\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Film City Hunter ini masih akan menampilkan petualangan Ryo Saeba, seorang <em>sweeper</em> atau detektif swasta yang menyelesaikan kasus kriminal di luar hukum kepolisian. Dua hal yang menjadikan Ryo sosok yang eksentrik adalah pistol Magnum miliknya, serta tingkahnya yang genit di depan wanita cantik.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49767\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49767\" data-attachment-id=\"49767\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-anime-city-hunter-kembali-hadir-di-tahun-2019/attachment/02-city-hunter/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-city-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-city-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-city-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-city-hunter.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49767 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-city-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"city hunter ryo\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-city-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-city-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49767\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ryo Saeba, sweeper ganjen. Sumber: Aniplex/Sunrise</p></div></p>\n<p>Seluruh pemeran <em>anime</em> City Hunter asli dari tahun 1987 akan kembali dalam film ini. Akira Kamiya kembali memerankan sosok Ryo Saeba, si detektif tangguh nan genit. Ryo menguasai berbagai teknik bertarung jarak dekat, kemampuan menggunakan berbagai jenis senjata api, hingga keahlian mengemudi tingkat tinggi. Wanita jadi kelemahan sekaligus kekuatan utama baginya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49768\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49768\" data-attachment-id=\"49768\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-anime-city-hunter-kembali-hadir-di-tahun-2019/attachment/03-city-hunter/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-city-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-city-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-city-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-city-hunter.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49768 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-city-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"city hunter kaori\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-city-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-city-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49768\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kaori Makimura, tukang palu. Sumber: Aniplex/Sunrise</p></div></p>\n<p>Kazue Ikura memerankan Kaori Makimura, rekan Ryo dalam bertugas. Kaori mengatur urusan administrasi hingga bertemu dengan klien yang butuh jasa Ryo. Meski demikian, Kaori juga mampu bertarung dan membela diri. Perempuan tomboi ini selalu jadi yang pertama “mendisiplinkan” Ryo jika dia terlalu terlena mengejar wanita cantik.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49769\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49769\" data-attachment-id=\"49769\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-anime-city-hunter-kembali-hadir-di-tahun-2019/attachment/04-city-hunter/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-city-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-city-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-city-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-city-hunter.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49769 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-city-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"city hunter saeko\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-city-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-city-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49769\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Saeko Nogami, polisi cantik. Sumber: Aniplex/Sunrise</p></div></p>\n<p>Karakter lainnya adalah Saeko Nogami yang diperankan Yoko Asagami. Saeko merupakan seorang detektif dari kepolisian Tokyo yang beberapa kali bekerja sama dengan Ryo dan Kaori dalam kasus-kasus rumit.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49770\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49770\" data-attachment-id=\"49770\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-anime-city-hunter-kembali-hadir-di-tahun-2019/attachment/05-city-hunter/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-city-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-city-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-city-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-city-hunter.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49770 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-city-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"city hunter umibozu\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-city-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-city-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49770\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Umibozu, saingan Ryo. Sumber: Aniplex/Sunrise</p></div></p>\n<p>Ada juga Umibozu yang diperankan Tessho Genda. Layaknya Ryo, Umibozu juga merupakan seorang <em>sweeper</em> yang kerja sambilan sebagai pelayan kafe. Umiobozu adalah saingan Ryo dalam bisnis <em>sweeper</em>, dan keduanya pun sama-sama tangguh. Berbeda dengan Ryo, Umibozu senang menggunakan senjata berat seperti senapan mesin hingga bazooka.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49771\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49771\" data-attachment-id=\"49771\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-anime-city-hunter-kembali-hadir-di-tahun-2019/attachment/06-city-hunter/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-city-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-city-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-city-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-city-hunter.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49771 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-city-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"city hunter miki\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-city-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/06-city-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49771\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Miki, bos dan pacar Umibozu. Sumber: Aniplex/Sunrise</p></div></p>\n<p>Terakhir, Mami Koyama berperan sebagai Miki. Ia adalah pemilik kafe Cat’s Eye yang jadi tempat kerja Umibozu. Miki merupakan teman seperjuangan Umibozu di masa lalu, dan keduanya pun merupakan sepasang kekasih.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49772\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49772\" data-attachment-id=\"49772\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-anime-city-hunter-kembali-hadir-di-tahun-2019/attachment/07-city-hunter/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-city-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-city-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-city-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-city-hunter.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49772 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-city-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"city hunter anime film\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-city-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/07-city-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49772\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Film City Hunter akan rilis tanggal 8 Februari 2019. Sumber: Aniplex/Sunrise</p></div></p>\n<p>Belum ada informasi seperti apa tepatnya cerita <em>anime</em> City Hunter ini. Namun, bisa dipastikan kisahnya akan menyesuaikan dengan era modern saat ini. Meski demikian, ciri khas serialnya masih akan dipertahankan, seperti palu raksasa yang dipakai Kaori untuk memukul Ryo, hingga mobil Mini Cooper khas milik Ryo.</p>\n<p>Nuansa City Hunter klasik juga masih akan dipertahankan karena sutradara Kenji Kodama yang menangani hampir semua <em>anime</em> City Hunter terdahulu akan mengarahkan film ini. Film ini juga akan menghadirkan komposer musik Taku Iwasaki yang terlibat dalam <em>anime</em> <em>spinoff</em> Angel Heart.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-summer-2018-harus-kamu-tonton/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">10 Anime Summer 2018 Yang Harus Kamu Tonton!</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Bukan Satu-satunya Film City Hunter di Tahun 2019</h2>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49773\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49773\" data-attachment-id=\"49773\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-anime-city-hunter-kembali-hadir-di-tahun-2019/attachment/08-city-hunter/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-city-hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08-city-hunter\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-city-hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-city-hunter.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49773 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-city-hunter.jpg\" alt=\"city hunter nicky larson\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-city-hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/08-city-hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49773\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nicky Larson adalah adaptasi Prancis dari City Hunter. Sumber: Linternaute</p></div></p>\n<p>Tahun 2019 juga akan menghadirkan berbagai adaptasi film City Hunter di berbagai negara! Di Prancis misalnya, akan ada film Nicky Larson yang tayang tanggal 6 Februari 2019, 2 hari lebih awal dari film <em>anime</em>nya. Nicky Larson, nama Prancis dari Ryo Saeba, akan diperankan oleh Philippe Lacheau yang juga menjadi sutradara film ini. Selain Nicky Larson, ada lagi film <em>live</em> <em>action</em> yang bakal dibuat di Cina dan tayang bulan Desember 2018 ini.</p>\n<p>Hmm, pasti penasaran kan dengan petualangan Ryo Saeba kali ini? Kamu suka seri yang mana: <em>anime</em>, <em>manga</em>, film <em>live action</em>, atau drama? Apa kamu berencana nonton film terbaru City Hunter versi <em>anime</em>, versi Prancis, atau versi Cina?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"edf4dc74-5762-57c7-b3c4-8b0f33c77557"}}}